Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许火星跟地球一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe that's what we're seeing on this other world as well.
