Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.59,0:42:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a chain of exploration
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.81,0:42:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大红斑现象的重要一环\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to understand that bright red dot in the dark night sky.
