Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.85,0:42:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道磁场是如何消失的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't t know how the magnetic field was lost.
