Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.00,0:42:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道甲烷的来源究竟是生命体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't know whether the methane is produced by life
